WEBVTT

00:00.920 --> 00:02.480
Your sister often warned me

00:02.800 --> 00:03.880
Since we are of the royal family

00:03.880 --> 00:05.000
Supported by the people

00:05.720 --> 00:06.280
We should

00:06.280 --> 00:08.040
Strive to restore Xuan

00:08.360 --> 00:09.920
Strive for the northern people

00:11.080 --> 00:12.600
Body not among men

00:13.080 --> 00:14.560
But heart fiercer than men

00:15.600 --> 00:16.800
When I recover the north

00:17.240 --> 00:19.040
She won't just be my empress

00:19.560 --> 00:21.400
But a hero of all Xuan

00:30.280 --> 00:31.000
Brother-in-law

00:31.880 --> 00:33.600
I also wish to be like my sister

00:34.080 --> 00:35.280
To establish the heart of heaven and earth

00:35.440 --> 00:36.600
To establish the destiny of the people

00:36.680 --> 00:37.560
For this chaotic age

00:37.920 --> 00:38.920
To open peace

00:41.680 --> 00:43.240
Please grant this, brother-in-law

00:43.800 --> 00:44.640
Good

00:45.120 --> 00:46.080
Since that's the case

00:47.080 --> 00:48.280
There's just one matter

00:48.600 --> 00:50.000
That only you can do

00:55.480 --> 00:56.640
This is what Sheng'er wrote

01:04.040 --> 01:06.080
Although there are still many areas needing improvement

01:06.640 --> 01:07.480
But I think

01:07.920 --> 01:09.360
You can help him perfect it

01:10.640 --> 01:11.800
You're his uncle

01:12.040 --> 01:12.760
This matter

01:13.080 --> 01:14.120
I only trust you

01:17.640 --> 01:18.440
I hope

01:18.680 --> 01:19.720
You'll go to Qingzhou

01:20.040 --> 01:21.080
To organize reforms

01:21.520 --> 01:22.920
Change the original land tax system

01:23.400 --> 01:24.640
From taxing by headcount

01:24.760 --> 01:26.000
To taxing by land

01:26.760 --> 01:27.440
In this way

01:27.600 --> 01:28.520
Those with more land

01:28.600 --> 01:29.520
Will pay more tax

01:29.960 --> 01:31.920
Those with less land can pay less tax

01:32.200 --> 01:33.080
If successful

01:33.960 --> 01:35.080
Then extend to the whole country

01:35.960 --> 01:37.200
Qingzhou

01:38.520 --> 01:39.280
That is

01:39.520 --> 01:41.040
Lady Chen's hometown

01:42.400 --> 01:43.080
What?

01:43.520 --> 01:44.560
Brother-in-law, don't worry

01:44.800 --> 01:45.640
This matter

01:46.400 --> 01:47.800
I will definitely do well

01:49.800 --> 01:50.680
I said

01:50.680 --> 01:51.680
Only talk about family matters

01:52.760 --> 01:53.440
Drink

01:57.400 --> 01:57.880
Come
